# Stray dev artifacts that don't belong in the repo.
# - Addon_Screenshots/: source images for the listings — big binaries,
#   the ones we actually ship live under docs/listings/screenshots/
# - Umbra.zip at repo root: a leftover from early testing; the real
#   distributed zips are built into frontend/public/ by the packager
# - scripts/batch_*_sampler.py etc: one-off research scripts we ran
#   to seed dungeon ability data. They contain a hardcoded admin
#   API key and write to C:/tmp — not production code. If we want
#   to retain the knowledge, sanitize first and move into scripts/samplers/
# - sync-addon.ps1: local dev convenience, Windows-specific
Addon_Screenshots/
Umbra.zip
scripts/batch_*_sampler.py
scripts/pass2_resample.py
scripts/propose_cooldowns.py
scripts/retry_cd_samples.py
scripts/cd_diff.py
sync-addon.ps1
